-- Fiat Will Hire Pomigliano Car Factory Workers in New Company, Ansa Reports
-- Tommaso Ebhardt
-- 2010-07-29T12:14:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-29/fiat-to-hire-pomigliano-car-factpru-workers-in-a-new-company-ansa-says.html

          
          
             Fiat SpA has formed a new company to
manage its Pomigliano plant in Italy, Ansa reported citing union
official Roberto di Maulo.  
 Fiat plans to hire Pomigliano workers under a new contract
accepted by all but one labor union  by the end of September,
Ansa said.  
          
          


  


        